{"tid":946974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京2019月曆日本熱賣　銷量超越「冰上王子」羽生結弦","createTime":"2018-12-19T02:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T06:46:55.000Z","uid":46245,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"542fa4ea368ab42dbb6da2452351bbcc6577de91","tid":946974,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20181217/s00005/1545043598034/%e6%99%ae%e4%ba%ac2019%e6%9c%88%e6%9b%86%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e7%86%b1%e8%b3%a3-%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e8%b6%85%e8%b6%8a%e3%80%8c%e5%86%b0%e4%b8%8a%e7%8e%8b%e5%ad%90%e3%80%8d%e7%be%bd%e7%94%9f%e7%b5%90%e5%bc%a6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00005%2F1545043598034%2F%25e6%2599%25ae%25e4%25ba%25ac2019%25e6%259c%2588%25e6%259b%2586%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e7%2586%25b1%25e8%25b3%25a3-%25e9%258a%25b7%25e9%2587%258f%25e8%25b6%2585%25e8%25b6%258a%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2586%25b0%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%258e%258b%25e5%25ad%2590%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%25be%25bd%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%25b5%2590%25e5%25bc%25a6&d=MgGw1fxvt6eEJPHkMJ7ZSgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1a38aa9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20181217%2Fs00005%2F1545043598034%2F%25e6%2599%25ae%25e4%25ba%25ac2019%25e6%259c%2588%25e6%259b%2586%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e7%2586%25b1%25e8%25b3%25a3-%25e9%258a%25b7%25e9%2587%258f%25e8%25b6%2585%25e8%25b6%258a%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2586%25b0%25e4%25b8%258a%25e7%258e%258b%25e5%25ad%2590%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%25be%25bd%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%25b5%2590%25e5%25bc%25a6&h=f6c93d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20181217/s00005/1545043598034/%e6%99%ae%e4%ba%ac2019%e6%9c%88%e6%9b%86%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e7%86%b1%e8%b3%a3-%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e8%b6%85%e8%b6%8a%e3%80%8c%e5%86%b0%e4%b8%8a%e7%8e%8b%e5%ad%90%e3%80%8d%e7%be%bd%e7%94%9f%e7%b5%90%e5%bc%a6</a><br />\n<br />\n日本有連鎖零售商表示，以俄羅斯總統普京照片為主題的2019年月曆在全國分店熱賣，銷量更超過知名男星及運動員。<br />\n<br />\n日本連鎖生活雜貨店Loft稱，普京的月曆最近在各地分店熱賣，日本男星田中圭，和有「冰上王子」之稱的花式滑冰運動員羽生結弦的月曆銷量，分別只排名第2及3位。普京的月曆內有多張他在工作以外的照片，例如寒冷天氣下浸冰水、坐上戰機、用健身器械訓練「操肌」等場景。<br />\n<br />\n有日本傳媒稱，很多購買普京月曆的人，包括大量女性在內，都被普京的非傳統風格和毫無顧忌的大男人主義所吸引。另有日本傳媒認為，部分人搶購普京月曆可能是出於惡作劇心態，但相信亦有部分人是真心對普京在克里姆林宮以外的個人生活很感興趣。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報）"},{"pid":"670f64194ec143ded94f9acbdc8f2c1bc8e4eb9c","tid":946974,"uid":34410,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkXdQcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkXdQcG.jpg&h=fcbc21ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普京大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a47bb7dbadb647ae9bcd83da21407e6e351a480","tid":946974,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdffc29ccbc7583a9f0c9cdcdd672dd01ee5cc9","tid":946974,"uid":56957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"有無維尼月曆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0641f631e8a706f56b1a8e236c3505d0f926d97e","tid":946974,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://loft.omni7.jp/search/?keyword=%E3%83%97%E3%83%BC%E3%83%81%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AB%E3%83%AC%E3%83%B3%E3%83%80%E3%83%BC&amp;searchKeywordFlg=1&amp;userKeywordFlg=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Floft.omni7.jp%2Fsearch%2F%3Fkeyword%3D%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%2581%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2582%25AB%25E3%2583%25AC%25E